    dc:date "2019" ;
    dc:title "Two new species of marine flatworm from southern China facilitate determination of the phylogenetic position of the genus Nerpa Marcus, 1948 and the histochemical structure of the nervous system in the genus Paucumara Sluys, 1989 (Platyhelminthes, Tricladida, Maricola)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2599330>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2599332>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2599336>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2599334>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2599338> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2599330>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Paucumara falcata. Live specimen: (A–B) entire animal; (C) testes and ovaries; (D) musculo-parenchymatic organ; (E) penis and vas deferentia. (F) cocoon. Scale bar: A–C, F = 200 µm; D–E = 20 µm;" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2599330/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2599332>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Paucumara falcata. Whole mounts. (A) PLA-N004, entire animal; (B) PLA-N004, testes and ovaries; (C) PLA- N006, penis and musculo-parenchymatic organ; (D) PLA-N005, musculo-parenchymatic organ. Scale bar: A–B = 200 µm, C– D = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2599332/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2599336>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Paucumara falcata. Diagrammatic horizontal reconstruction: (A) entire animal; (B) copulatory apparatus, based on examination of several specimens; ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2599336/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2599334>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Paucumara falcata. Photomicrographs: (A) PLA-Pa002, testes; (B–C) PLA-Pa002, penis and musculoparenchymatic organ; (D) PLA-Pa002, female reproductive system; (E) PLA-Pa001, oviducts and bursal canal. Scale bar: 20 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2599334/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2599338>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Paucumara falcata. (A) diagrammatic reconstruction of the copulatory apparatus, based on examination of several specimens; (B) two animals in copulation. Scale bar: 500 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2599338/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

